  "texts": [
    "Therefore, we use Modified Correct to remove the above influence.",
    "We have redesigned the validation method, comparing and analyzing the results extracted from the large model with those annotated by experts, and calculating specific indicators based on binary classification.",
    "The calculation method is shown in the Fig. 4.To the best of our knowledge, CataLM is the first work to use LLMs for extracting knowledge content in the field of photocatalysis.",
    "However, in the field of materials, some scholars have used supervised intelligent methods to assist in the recognition of material entities.",
    "Wang et al. [43] proposed CHEMNER, an ontology guided, distantly-supervised method for fine grained chemistry NER, and achieved 45.96% F1."
